---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy | Sam Jolley"
  description="How samjolley.com handles your data. Short version: it does not collect any."
>
  <h1>Privacy</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    Short version: this site does not collect your personal data.
  </p>

  <h2>What this site collects</h2>
  <p>
    Nothing. samjolley.com is a static website with no accounts, no forms, no
    cookies, and no analytics or third-party trackers.
  </p>

  <h2>Hosting</h2>
  <p>
    The site is hosted on GitHub Pages. Like any web host, GitHub may log
    standard technical request information such as IP address and browser type
    for security and reliability. That data is handled under
    <a
      href="https://docs.github.com/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"
      rel="noopener">GitHub's privacy statement</a
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>Links to other services</h2>
  <p>
    This site links to external services such as GitHub, LinkedIn, and
    ZeroBeatLabs. This site does not embed their content or send them
    information before you choose a link. Their privacy policies apply after
    you follow a link.
  </p>

  <h2>If you email me</h2>
  <p>
    If you contact me at
    <a href="mailto:hello@zerobeatlabs.org">hello@zerobeatlabs.org</a>, I use
    your message and email address only to reply. I do not add you to any
    mailing list, and I do not share your details.
  </p>

  <h2>No selling or sharing</h2>
  <p>I do not sell, rent, or share personal information.</p>

  <p>Last updated 18 July 2026.</p>
</Base>
